ere the latest Wi-Fi standard, IEEE 802.11ax, will coexist with the\nlatest cellular technology, 5G New Radio (NR) in unlicensed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Dec 2021 18:01:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-30"}
